# Substack Article – Day 05

## Title:
Why Community Ownership Makes BubuVerse Special

## Summary:
In today’s Substack article, I explore how BubuVerse is designed around *community ownership* — explaining how real participation, collective decision-making, and shared assets make the ecosystem sustainable.

